sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuário
    participant R as React
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant L as C++ DLL
    participant TP as ThreadPool
    participant RPA as RPA Engine
    participant JSON as Storage

    U->>R: Abrir aplicação
    R->>API: GET /machine-id
    API-->>R: Retorna ID

    U->>R: Enviar chave
    R->>API: POST /validate
    API->>L: Validar(ID, chave)
    L-->>API: 1 ou 0
    API-->>R: Status da licença

    U->>R: Upload Excel + Iniciar
    R->>API: POST /start
    API->>TP: Submeter tarefa

    TP->>RPA: Executar automação
    RPA->>JSON: Atualizar histórico
    RPA-->>API: Resultado
    API-->>R: SSE progresso
